*{{citation |last=Davitt |first=Jacqueline |title=Witches and Ghosts of Pendle and the Ribble Valley |place=Stroud |publisher=Tempus |year=2006 |isbn=0-7524-4063-2}}
*{{citation |last=Douglas |first=Arthur |title=The Fate of the Lancashire Witches |year=1978 |place=Chorley |publisher=Countryside Publications |isbn=0-86157-001-4}}
