*{{citation |last=Swain |first=John |contribution=Witchcraft, Economy and Society in the Forest of Pendle |editor-last=Poole |editor-first=Robert |title=The Lancashire Witches: Histories and Stories |publisher=Manchester University Press |year=2002 |isbn=978-0-7190-6204-9 |pages=73–87}}
